  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Leader. You lead by shielding allies with your prayers, healing, and using powers that improve your allies' attacks.</p><p><strong>Power Source:</strong> Divine. You have been invested with the authority to wield divine power on behalf of a deity, faith, or philosophy.</p><p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Wisdom</p></li><li><p>Strength</p></li><li><p>Charisma</p></li></ul><p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.LEPCRMtCimzvXr25]{Chainmail}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.kjW9S8gIQ0LBMF53]{Simple Melee Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.G50MDDGV8v1NRT9u]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Implements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.NZq50Sq6slOAaX29]{Holy Symbol}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p><ul><li><p>+2 Will</p></li></ul><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level: [[12]] + Con Score</strong></p><p><strong>Hit Points per Level Gained: [[5]]</strong></p><p><strong>Base Healing Surges per Day: [[7]] + Con Mod</strong></p><p><strong>Skill Training: </strong>Religion, choose three more from the following list:</p><ul><li><p>Arcana (Int)</p></li><li><p>Diplomacy(Cha)</p></li><li><p>Healing (Wis)</p></li><li><p>History (Int)</p></li><li><p>Insight (Wis)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Channel Divinity</p></li><li><p>Healer's Lore</p></li><li><p>Healing Word</p></li><li><p>Ritual Casting</p></li></ul>",
